* Beware: Notebooks

Notebooks are great:

- shiny
- easy
- slick
- a web page!

But they are no panacea.
They can also be quite treacherous, deceptive and unreliable.

See:

.link https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1n2RlMdmv1p25Xy5thJUhkKGvjtV-dkAIsUXP-AL4ffI/edit#slide=id.g362da58057_0_1 "I Don't Like Notebooks - Joel Grus - #JupyterCon 2018"
